title: Client keeps sending me to the homescreen
body:
Every queue pop I get sent to the homescreen when a queue pops and I click accept. the game is there, it's happening behind the homescreen, I just can't see it or select anything - and if I let the timer go out I get the game leave warning. 
30 minute ban when I'm trying to kill time until my train. Please, I have an hour and a half before breakfast places open.
